<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Festschrift">Festschrift</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=John_Barton_(theologian)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Festschrift"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ol><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFDellJoyce2013" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Katharine_J._Dell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Katharine J. Dell (page does not exist)">Dell, Katharine J.</a>; <a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_M._Joyce&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Paul M. Joyce (page does not exist)">Joyce, Paul M.</a>, eds. (2013). <i>Biblical Interpretation and Method: essays in honour of John Barton</i>. Oxford: Oxford University Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780199645534" title="Special:BookSources/9780199645534"><bdi>9780199645534</bdi></a>. <a href="/wiki/OCLC_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="OCLC (identifier)">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/857990808">857990808</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Biblical+Interpretation+and+Method%3A+essays+in+honour+of+John+Barton&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F857990808&amp;rft.isbn=9780199645534&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJohn+Barton+%28theologian%29" class="Z3988"></span></li></ol>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Personal_life">Personal life</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=John_Barton_(theologian)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Personal life"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>In 1973, Barton married Mary Burn. Together they have one daughter.<sup id="cite_ref-WW_2018_2-10" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-WW_2018-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>
</p><p>Barton lives in the parish of <a href="/wiki/Abingdon-on-Thames" title="Abingdon-on-Thames">Abingdon</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-modernchurch_12-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-modernchurch-12">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
